## About
DEPRECIATED for platform-monorepo. the Steve Jobs 'Intention Engine' concept into a deterministic execution engine. It replaces unpredictable LLM chatter with a closed-loop system that parses intent, validates environmental constraints, and requires explicit user confirmation before manipulating real-world APIs
